channel.title: Webclient No Work For Others?
channel.description:
Hi, I just got my server working on my windows 7 computer, i had lots of client problems, now with the help of mopar users I have no errors now, I can run the server on windows 7 and also compile it, but now my last problem is the webclient, I have made my webclient and I can access but others cant, I hosted it on webs,com as always but it seems to be a problem with others logging on, can any one help me out?
In a nut shell: *I CAN LOG IN VIA WINDOWS 7 PC *I CAN LOG IN VIA WINDOWS VISTA LAPTOP *BOTH MY LAPTOP + PC HAVE THE CACHE *OTHERS SAY THEY CANT EVEN MAKE IT TO THE LOGIN SCREEN, OR THEY CANT LOG IN
HELP ME PLEASE
I used this to host my client.jar: Hells-History,webs,com/
(server is offline for now so no 1 can log in).
I would apreesiate if anyone gave me the applet code for HTML with the client embeded working for all! THANKS </3
Server Base: Rune-Live, PI (btw. was i supposed to upload key store aswell? because i didnt.. :s)
